  <h3 class="about-h3">Projects</h3>
  <div class="about-projects">
    <div class="about-project-item">
      <h4 class="about-project-name">1. YatraStay - Accommodation Booking Platform</h4>
      <p class="about-p1">
        <strong>Overview:</strong> YatraStay is a full-stack accommodation booking platform inspired by
        modern travel and stay applications. It enables users to search, explore, and book properties while
        allowing hosts to list and manage their accommodations. The platform is designed to handle real-world
        booking workflows with a focus on scalability, security, and user experience.
      </p>
      <p class="about-p1"><strong>Features:</strong></p>
      <ul class="about-feature-list">
        <li>User authentication and authorization with secure access control.</li>
        <li>Advanced property search based on location, price, and amenities.</li>
        <li>Filtering, sorting, and pagination for large datasets.</li>
        <li>Property listing and management for hosts.</li>
        <li>Booking management with reservation tracking and wishlist support.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="about-p1"><strong>Technologies:</strong></p>
      <div class="about-tech-list">
        <span class="about-tech">React</span>
        <span class="about-tech">Node.js</span>
        <span class="about-tech">Express</span>
        <span class="about-tech">MongoDB</span>
        <span class="about-tech">JWT</span>
        <span class="about-tech">REST APIs</span>
        <span class="about-tech">Tailwind CSS</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-project-item">
      <h4 class="about-project-name">2. Authentication and Authorization System</h4>
      <p class="about-p1">
        <strong>Overview:</strong> This project is a secure and reusable authentication and authorization system
        for modern web applications. It focuses on OTP-based email verification, token-based authentication, and
        role-based access control while following security best practices.
      </p>
      <p class="about-p1"><strong>Features:</strong></p>
      <ul class="about-feature-list">
        <li>User registration and login with secure password hashing.</li>
        <li>OTP-based email verification using SMTP integration.</li>
        <li>JWT-based authentication and session management.</li>
        <li>Role-based access control and protected API routes.</li>
        <li>Input validation, error handling, and token expiration handling.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="about-p1"><strong>Technologies:</strong></p>
      <div class="about-tech-list">
        <span class="about-tech">Node.js</span>
        <span class="about-tech">Express</span>
        <span class="about-tech">MongoDB</span>
        <span class="about-tech">JWT</span>
        <span class="about-tech">Nodemailer</span>
      </div>
    </div>

