      <p class="about-p1">
        <strong>Overview:</strong> This project is a full-stack e-commerce platform that simulates real-world
        online shopping workflows. It lets users browse products, manage carts, place orders, and track purchases
        while enabling admins to manage operations from a central dashboard.
      </p>
      <p class="about-p1"><strong>Features:</strong></p>
      <ul class="about-feature-list">
        <li>Product search, filtering, and category-based browsing.</li>
        <li>Shopping cart, wishlist, and secure user account management.</li>
        <li>Mock payment integration for checkout.</li>
        <li>Order placement, tracking, and history.</li>
        <li>Admin dashboard for products, customers, orders, and analytics.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="about-p1"><strong>Technologies:</strong></p>
